		{"id":"32b05fe1a1cba6c6","type":"text","text":"#### 安裝\n\n```bash\npip install apache-airflow\n```\n\n#### 設定環境變數\n\n```plaintext\nexport AIRFLOW_HOME=~/airflow\n```","x":-651,"y":170,"width":356,"height":338},
